        <body>       

                <pb n="1"/>
            <p>My dear Doctor<lb/></p>
            <p>I found your letter on<lb/> my arrival yesterday from Newport.<lb/></p>
            <p>I sent revised curr<hi rend="sup">m</hi>. to Mr Cowan last night.<lb/>  It is materially changed from ours.<lb/></p>
            <p>I enclose letter from Mr B. this a. m. rec<hi rend="sup">d</hi>.<lb/>  If you cannot come next Sunday<lb/> please send me <hi rend="underline">full</hi> particulars.<lb/>  i. e. <hi rend="underline">full instructions&#44;</hi> as to sessions etc.&#45;&#45;<lb/></p>
            <p>Yrs<lb/>
                Pereira Mendes<lb/></p>
            <p>Aug 28&#47;88<lb/></p>
            <p>Thanks for good wishes.  They<lb/> are <sic>sincery</sic> reciprocated&#44;&#45;&#45;but<lb/> I shall write no doubt before<lb/> Rosh Ashana<lb/></p>
                
            <p>Please write me at once so that I can see Dr Drachman before Sunday&#44;&#45;&#45;say W&#39;dnesday<lb/></p>
            </body>
    </text>
